name: "Giant Chicken of Washington" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Paint pen and liner pen on reclaimed cardboard with digital embellishments and colors.] Deep in the forests and mountains of Washington State lives a gigantic, prehistoric creature that brings terror to the hearts of the toughest logger or park ranger: The Giant Chicken of Washington!!! When in these primordial woods, always beware the clucking... ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
